  "script": [
    {
      "type": "scene",
      "text": "对话一：奶茶店——王崩和小黑 (Boba Shop — Wang Beng and Xiao Hei)",
      "en": "Dialogue 1: Boba shop -- 王崩 and 小黑."
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "text": "奶茶店。面对面坐着。王崩点了一杯很复杂的，盯着看，表情狐疑。",
      "en": "Boba shop. Sitting face to face. 王崩 orders something complicated, stares at it, expression suspicious."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "你在看你的奶茶像在看合同。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "珍珠分布不均匀。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "……喝就是了。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "好喝吗？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "……可以。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "\"可以\"。你的夸人技术真incredible。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "台北有一家叫——"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "用掉了。你的一次机会用掉了。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "我还没说完。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "你要说台北的一家奶茶店。算了。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "……好吧。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "你为什么用那个美白霜？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "……什么？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "那个霜。脸上的。提亮什么的。为什么？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "因为……中国的审美标准。我太黑了。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "你不黑。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "你说起来容易。你皮肤白。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "我是台湾人。一样的太阳。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "……皮肤颜色不是这样work的。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "我知道。我的意思是——你的皮肤不是问题。标准是问题。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "……"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "这是你对我说的第二次好话。第一次是外套。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "我不是在说好话。我在说事实。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "对你来说，一样的。"
    },
    {
      "type": "scene",
      "text": "对话二：广东菜——矮中和清清 (Cantonese Food — Ai Zhong and Qingqing)",
      "en": "Dialogue 2: Cantonese food -- 矮中 and 清清."
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "text": "这个星期他们每天都在图书馆学习了。一开始是做作业。现在矮中没有作业也来。",
      "en": "This week they've studied at the library every day. At first it was for homework. Now 矮中 comes even when there's no homework."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "学完了想不想去吃饭？不是火锅。正经吃饭。我找到了一家广东菜，据说很好吃。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "你找了一家广东菜？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "本来是为小黑找的。但她在跟王崩约会了。所以……"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "所以我是备选？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "不是！我是说——我想带你去。但是如果你说不我就用小黑当借口。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "……这很pathetic。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "我知道。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "……好。走吧。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "……真的？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "别让我说第二遍。"
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "text": "餐厅。矮中点菜了——用中文，没看英文菜单。清清看着。他的中文在变好。什么时候的事？",
      "en": "Restaurant. 矮中 orders -- in Chinese, no English menu. 清清 watches. His Chinese is getting better. When did that happen?"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "好吃吗？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "好吃到爆。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "你刚才说好吃到爆了吗？清清——全宇宙最proper的人——刚才用了slang？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "这是完全valid的表达。",
      "sub": "脸红"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "你是从我这里学的！"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "我没——"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "你肯定是！我教了你slang！这是我最骄傲的moment！"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "吃你的饭，矮中。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "是！"
    },
    {
